                    <span>Jason Hunter has done it again. His servlet chapter is simply awesome. He offers some really juicy bytes of information. Give the man more chapters. The other chapters are good too. I would give the book five stars but the Performance chapter is worthless. That came as a surprise because I enjoyed Jack Shirazi performance book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">excellent source when time is not on your side</div>
